{
  "stem": "22869.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They want somebody should be an escort to them, to come along to the American lines and tell the Americans that they were very nice to us, that they protected us, that they were good to us.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Of course, nobody wanted to do it because first of all, we're afraid the first one jumps out of the train, he'll take the rifle and bingo.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's it, trying to escape.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we were very reluctant to give in or-- or show any kind of emotions to them, and we were just playing the waiting game.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, the shooting was going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were here starving to death, hungry, thirsty, and-- and we didn't know what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the fifth of May-- on the fifth of May, we get up in the morning.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's no SS guard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We look out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody sees an SS guard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We used to yell, we'll yell over to the other-- hey, fellows, does anybody see a guard?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody sees a guard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So little by little, one or two guys started jumping out of the train, one by one, one by one, one--.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No guard.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nobody's being shot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nobody's--.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So by the time we saw that it's really the-- you know, everything is clear, so somebody started yelling on top of his-- of his lungs, hey, fellow, we're free.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I don't have to explain you what happened at that minute.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, we broke up in a jovial dance and crying.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a funny thing that then, more than ever, at that time we were crying for happiness than smiling and laughing for happiness.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That every second that we felt [SOBBING] that this is it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is freedom.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The-- the tears were pouring from the eyes like crazy.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
